# 📊 Bank Marketing Campaign — Funnel & Conversion Performance Analysis
### Data Science & Analytics – Task 3 | Future Interns Internship Program 2026

---

## 🔍 Project Overview

This project analyzes a real-world bank marketing campaign dataset to understand how clients move through the marketing funnel — from first contact to subscription. The goal is to identify where drop-offs occur, which segments convert best, and what actions can improve campaign performance.

This analysis reflects the kind of work done by marketing analysts and growth teams at banks, fintech companies, and subscription businesses.

---

##  Business Questions Answered

- What is the overall campaign conversion rate?
- Where are clients dropping off in the funnel?
- Which months have the highest conversion rates?
- Which job types and education levels convert best?
- Does calling clients more times improve conversion?
- How does account balance influence subscription likelihood?

