## ✅ Business Recommendations

| Recommendation | Target Segment |
|---------------|---------------|
| Focus campaign efforts in March, September & October | All clients |
| Limit contact attempts to maximum 3 calls per client | Over-contacted clients |
| Prioritize retired and student segments for outreach | Job-based targeting |
| Offer tailored products to high-balance clients | High-balance segment |
| Re-engage clients who converted in previous campaigns | Poutcome = success |
| Review and improve approach for clients with negative balances | Negative balance segment |

